er-radius: 4px; color: rgb(138, 109, 59); font-family: Lato; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(252, 248, 227);"><span style="font-size:16px">Streams are no longer sorted by KBps. Read our&nbsp;<a href="http://www.streamsports.me/news/" style="color: rgb(207, 181, 51); box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;" title="StreamSports news">website news.</a></span></div>\n\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px; font-family: Lato; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);">\n<div class="col-sm-6" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 585px;">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n', '1');
