(227, 133710, 'Nancy', 1967, 'Soccer', 'French Ligue 2', '4401', 'Pablo Correa', '', '', '', 'Stade Marcel Picot is a football (soccer) stadium located in Tomblaine, France, near the city of Nancy. Built in 1926, it is used by Ligue 1 soccer team AS Nancy.\r\n\r\nThe stadium was completely rebuilt and inaugurated in its new configuration in 2003. It is now able to hold 20,087 people.\r\n\r\nSince summer 2010, Marcel-Picot is one of the very few French stadiums equipped with artificial turf.', 'Tomblaine', 'www.asnl.net', 'www.facebook.com/asnancylorraine', 'twitter.com/asnlofficiel', 'instagram.com/asnl_officiel', '', 'http://www.thesportsdb.com/images/media/team/badge/ssqsyy1427138028.png', 'http://www.thesportsdb.com/images/media/team/jersey/ssxwvp1423797743.png', ''),
