(229, 134711, 'Niort', 1925, 'Soccer', 'French Ligue 2', '4401', 'RÃ©gis Brouard', '', '', '', 'Stade RenÃ© Gaillard is a multi-use stadium in Niort, France.\r\n\r\nIt is the home of French Championnat de France amateur football team Chamois Niortais and has a capacity of 10,898 spectators. Niort played their first game at the Stade RenÃ© Gaillard on 3 August 1974.\r\n\r\nThe record attendance at the stadium is 16,715 for the game between Chamois Niortais and Olympique Marseille in 1988.', 'Niort', 'www.chamoisniortais.fr', 'fr-fr.facebook.com/pages/Chamois-Niortais-Officiel', 'twitter.com/CNFC_Officiel', '', '', 'http://www.thesportsdb.com/images/media/team/badge/swqxpq1426871083.png', 'http://www.thesportsdb.com/images/media/team/jersey/ysvuus1423797879.png', ''),
