(535, 134432, 'Krylya Sovetov Samara', 1942, 'Soccer', 'Russian Football Premier League ', '4355', 'Franky Vercauteren', '', '', '', 'Metallurg Stadium (Russian: Â«ÐœÐµÑ‚Ð°Ð»Ð»ÑƒÑ€Ð³Â») is a football stadium in Samara, Russia and is home to Russian Premier League club FC Krylia Sovetov. Built in 1957, Metallurg Stadium has a capacity of 33,001 seats since its latest renovation. It has also been repeatedly awarded the VCSPS Diploma, which rates the quality of all sport complexes in Russia.', 'Samara', 'eng.kc-camapa.ru/cgi-bin/stadium.cgi', 'www.facebook.com/kccamapa', 'twitter.com/fckssamara', 'instagram.com/fckssamara', '', 'http://www.thesportsdb.com/images/media/team/badge/yvqyxw1447540450.png', '', ''),
