(783, 134962, 'AmDTuning.com', 2010, 'Motorsport', 'BTCC', '4372', 'Shaun Hollamby', '', '', '', 'The company was formed in 1987, specialising in the Volkswagen-Audi marque, forming their own VW-backed race team in 1990. They went on to win many championships with AmD-built and tuned Volkswagen Golfs. The company now offers tuning parts for most European cars.\r\n\r\nFor the 2008 & 2009 season AmD ran SEAT LeÃ³ns in the Dunlop Sportmaxx Cup and won the championship in 2009, with Simon Shaw driving.', 'West Thurrock', 'www.amdtuning.com', 'www.facebook.com/AmDTuning', 'twitter.com/amdessex', '', '', 'http://www.thesportsdb.com/images/media/team/badge/wttuqr1432775111.png', 'http://www.thesportsdb.com/images/media/team/jersey/tystwu1432774995.png', ''),
