(793, 134952, 'Pirtek Racing', 1987, 'Motorsport', 'BTCC', '4372', 'Mike Jordan', '', '', '', 'Eurotech Racing is a British motor racing team based in Tamworth, Staffordshire and founded by Mike Jordan. The team races under the Pirtek Racing banner in the British Touring Car Championship.\r\n\r\nThe team won both the BTCC independent teams trophy and the independent drivers championship with Andrew Jordan in 2012.', 'Tamworth, Staffordshire', 'www.pirtek.co.uk', '', 'www.twitter.com/andyjordanbtcc', '', '', 'http://www.thesportsdb.com/images/media/team/badge/xrvsxx1432776335.png', 'http://www.thesportsdb.com/images/media/team/jersey/rvuywu1432776198.png', 'http://www.thesportsdb.com/images/media/team/logo/xryvuv1432776373.png'),
