(1127, 135097, 'Valencia Basket', 1986, 'Basketball', 'Spanish Liga ACB', '4408', '', '', '', '', 'PabellÃ³n Municipal Fuente San Luis (known as la Fonteta) is an arena in Valencia, Spain. Built in 1983, it is primarily used for basketball and the home arena of Valencia BC and the women team Ros Casares Valencia. The arena has a seating capacity for 9,000 people.', 'Valencia', 'www.valenciabasket.com', 'www.facebook.com/valenciabasket', 'twitter.com/valenciabasket', '', '', 'http://www.thesportsdb.com/images/media/team/badge/ywrpsy1427139685.png', '', ''),
