(36, 'Technology', 'technology', 'Equinix London LD4 Forex Trading | Technology Server - MetaTrader 4', 'Fastest trading server at the heart of London Financial district with state of the art Equinix LD4 technology providing lighting fast execution speed.', 'Equinix, LD4 , London, forex execution, MT4', '', '<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/BlackBull%20technology.jpg" style="height:223px; width:850px" /></span></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">In a market where &ldquo;top of the line technology&rdquo; is used by a large proportion of the trading industry, we give our clients the ultimate trading advantage. We work hard to get the best technology before it&rsquo;s released as well as having a focus on development of our own unique proprietary technology. &nbsp;Our execution speeds are a top priority, so we have placed our trading servers in the heart of the London financial district, connected by Fiber Optic cable. &nbsp;Our servers also run on institutional grade high load servers removing the possibility of a bottleneck on our end.</span></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">London LD4 Equinox Data Centre</span></li>\n<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">State of the Art Technology infrastructure</span></li>\n<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">Direct fiber optic connection to Liquidity Provider (Tier1 banks)</span></li>\n<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">Sub-milliseconds execution speed.</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">This means our clients get a rare sense of raw execution not found in many places outside major hedge funds and investment banks. Further, these lightning fast servers allow us to use multi-tiered best bid/offer aggregation technology. This means using multiple liquidity providers by constantly processing the live interbank spread quotes. When you place a trade it is processed to the cheapest current liquidity provider we have in our system to make sure you get the best possible price available. All of these systems and algorithms running through our servers mean that no matter which trading platform you use, our execution engine facilitates a highly efficient integration of data and information flow every time a trade is placed.</span></p>\n\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><br />\n<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">While there are many good platforms out there in the market, we feel there can still be improvements made. This is why we currently are constructing our own platform in order to meet experienced trader requirements at the institutional level, as well as giving our new clients the best chance of profiting, which is exciting for everyone. These key pieces of technology contribute to our client&rsquo;s power in the market, for which BlackBull Markets is known and regarded in the industry.</span><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-02-24 00:00:00', ''),
