(38, 'White Label', 'white-label', 'Best White Label Program | Start your Forex Brokerage - BlackBull Markets', 'Grow your forex business with  BlackBull Markets White Label Program ', 'White label, start your brokerage , forex trading, forex broker,  custom branding', '', '<p><img alt="" src="http://s5.postimg.org/lz3hsjp07/image.jpg" style="height:180px; width:880px" /></p>\n\n<p>BlackBull Markets institutional grade White-Label services and technologies provide a complete solution for FX Brokers to manage and streamline their businesses, while increasing profitability and preserving free choice of liquidity.</p>\n\n<p><strong><u>Key benefits:</u></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>One-stop offering which combines technology with hosting and administration.</li>\n<li>Free choice of liquidity.</li>\n<li>Supplementary software bundles (One-Click Trading, Mobile Trader, MAM, News Feed &hellip;)</li>\n<li>Reduce initial capital requirements and operational costs.</li>\n<li>Reduce in-house technical know-how and overhead.</li>\n<li>24/5 dedicated technical support.</li>\n</ul>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-03-01 00:00:00', ''),
(39, 'Money Manager', 'money-manager', 'Fund Manager Forex Trading | MAM, PAMM | Manage Multiple Trading Accounts - BlackBull Markets', 'BlackBull Markets provides exclusive money manager program. Asset Manager can manage multiple account via one single platform', 'MAM, PAMM, money manager, fund manager, asset manager , forex manager, forex broker, ', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/Money%20manager.jpg" /></p>\n\n<p>Our BlackBull Markets institutional division has a solution for money managers and hedge funds also known as MAM or Multi Account Manager. This is an integrated software tool to execute trades in a quick manner from your master trading account to your clients individual trading accounts. While you can offer your solutions on autotrade, this method can be done in house while giving you more privacy.&nbsp;&nbsp; In turn, this gives you more of a professional angle of managing other accounts and having clients of your own.</p>\n\n<p>The platform is designed to trade through the BlackBull Markets MT4 platform.&nbsp; The trades are processed on our servers in <strong>Equinox London</strong> allowing for lightening fast reliable trading. &nbsp;This means that an unlimited number of accounts can be traded with just a simple click of the mouse.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Easily manage Monthly, Quarterly, and Annual client reports. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n<li>MT Manager3 allocation methods - Lot, Percentage, Proportional.</li>\n<li>Manage multiple master accounts having different strategies.</li>\n<li>Unlimited number of customer accounts.</li>\n<li>Monitor commissions and performance in realtime.</li>\n<li>Allows Expert Advisor (EA) trading.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://s5.postimg.org/rn575p3yv/blackbull_mam.jpg" style="line-height:20.7999992370605px" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>If <strong>you are interested</strong> in learning more, or setting up MAM, please <strong>contact a member of the BlackBull Markets Staff</strong>&nbsp;and we will set that up for you. &nbsp;For accounts over $10,000, no additional fees apply.</p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-03-01 00:00:00', ''),
(40, 'Live Webinar', 'live-webinar', 'Live Webinars | Seminars - Sponsored by BlackBull Markets', '', 'Webinars , Seminars, forex broker , forex trading ', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/Webinars.jpg" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Complete the form below for when our next live Webinars are happening:&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style="color:rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family:open sans,helvetica,arial,sans-serif">%%webinar-z9osot54-1%/%</span></p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-02-21 00:00:00', ''),
(41, 'Getting Started', 'getting-started', 'Getting Started | Forex Trading - BlackBull Markets', '', 'trading forex , getting started, forex trading, ', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/start%20learning.jpg" /></p>\n\n<p><strong>What is FX Trading?</strong></p>\n\n<p>In the global financial markets, &ldquo;FX&rdquo; or &ldquo;Forex&rdquo; trading occurs in the foreign exchange marketplace and is used to exchange one currency for another.&nbsp; &nbsp;I am sure when you go to the bank you can see all of the different rates on the window and that is what those different currencies convert to at any given time. &nbsp;Trading the FX market provides a large number of trading opportunities due to the vast magnitude of inter-day transactional volume. As a trader you can enter contracts or trades on either the buy or sell directions (buy if you think one currency will strengthen and go up versus another, or sell if you think it will go down on the pair).</p>\n\n<p>This market also give many more opportunities to trade around your schedule as it is open 24 hours a day, 5.5 days a week.&nbsp; At BlackBull Markets, our clients have access to different amounts of leverage that translates into purchasing power.&nbsp; This means that smaller moves in the market can be as profitable as the larger ones.&nbsp; Using this leverage, our clients can speculate and profit from global currency flows as different currencies increase and decrease in value with volatility.&nbsp; The key advantage with the Forex market is due to it currently being the largest market and most liquid financial market in the world.&nbsp; It is many times larger than the New York and London stock exchanges combined.&nbsp; The fact that it is open 24 hours a day to trade, has a decentralized structure, and low barriers to entry, trading the Forex market through BlackBull Markets allows and provides the key opportunity for clients to trade using many different styles on their terms.&nbsp; This allows for the highest profit making potential and lifestyle balance.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Trading FX works by traders hoping to generate profits or income by speculating on the future value of one currency to another.&nbsp; This means that currencies are always traded as pairs.&nbsp; Trading FX in different combinations offers a vast amount of opportunities to profit from.&nbsp; The exchange rates change between different global currencies. &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Example:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Let&#39;s say for example you purchase 10,000 euros with US dollars at the EUR/USD (this is code for the pair) at an exchange rate of 1.1800. &nbsp;This means that you have exchanged 11,800 USD to buy 10,000 euros thinking that the Euro will increase in value over the US dollar.&nbsp; The next day you were right and the current exchange rate has changed in your favor to 1.2500.&nbsp; So you then exchange your 10,000 euros back into US Dollars, but now you have 12,500 having only paid 11,800.&nbsp; This means the difference is 700 dollars of profit. Simply put, your Euros have become worth more so when converting them back they have gone up 700 dollars in value.&nbsp; This is the theory of what goes on when you place your trades.&nbsp; If math isn&#39;t your strong suit due to how fast some trading decisions need to be made then that&rsquo;s OK.&nbsp; The actual trading platforms we offer at BlackBull markets make it very simple.&nbsp; With just a click of a button, our clients can decide how large a position they want to buy in a pair, placing the order, or closing the trade. You can learn more about this in the education section, which will take you from knowing nothing, to giving you strategies on how to trade the FX markets with amazing success!</p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-03-01 00:00:00', ''),
(49, 'Why BlackBull Markets', 'why-blackbull-markets', 'Trade Forex Gold Silver and Oil | BlackBull Markets', 'BlackBull Markets provide tightest spreads, lighting fast execution speed, best technology infrastructure and world class customer service. ', 'Voted best Customer Support, raw spreads, risk-free demo trading account ', '', '<h2 dir="ltr"><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/Money%20manager%20SMALL.jpg" style="height:227px; width:850px" /></h2>\n\n<h2 dir="ltr">Our Vision</h2>\n\n<p dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p dir="ltr">BlackBull Markets is landing instutional level investment opportunities to the every client who trades with us.</p>\n\n<p dir="ltr">We further aim to give instutional levels of service to our clients where a client has a personal broker and analyst allocated to assist them in their needs.</p>\n\n<p dir="ltr">Finally BlackBull Markets technology goes above and beyond what is currently standard by implimenting new and faster ways of trading to make sure your orders get filled faster and cheaper then anywhere else.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.blackbullmarkets.com/content/view/technology" target="_blank"><strong>Click Here</strong></a> to learn more about our BlackBull Technology</p>\n\n<p dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2 dir="ltr">Auto Trade&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<h2 dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.blackbullmarkets.com/content/view/myfxbook-auto-trade" style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/auto%20trade%20homepage%281%29.jpg" style="height:216px; width:849px" /></a></h2>\n\n<p dir="ltr">Copy trades from best performing hand picked traders to your BlackBull Markets trading platform.</p>\n\n<ul dir="ltr">\n<li>Choose From Multiple Traders to Copy</li>\n<li>Accurate Statistics - Performance reporting audited.</li>\n<li>Maintain Control on Profit and Risk.</li>\n<li>Easy to Add and Remove Traders.</li>\n<li>Hand Picked Strategies by the autotrade team.</li>\n<li>Trade your MT4 account as per normal alongside signals.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><a href="https://www.blackbullmarkets.com/content/view/myfxbook-auto-trade" target="_blank"><strong>Click Here</strong></a> to visit our Auto Trade page.</p>\n\n<h2 dir="ltr">&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<h2 dir="ltr">Institutional Analyst Service</h2>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/Analyst%281%29.jpg" style="height:242px; width:850px" /></p>\n\n<p>BlackBull Markets has partnered with Instutional Analysts to give our live clients a morning newsletter with an outlook on key markets and where the&nbsp;price might be going.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Further our clients have access to market updates every 2 hours on major trading pairs and commodities.</p>\n\n<p>This can be accessed on our website and on our trading platform for speed and ease.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul></ul>\n\n<p>Daily FX Technical Strategy Newsletter</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Trading Central Instutional level Technical Analysis Strategies.</li>\n<li>Covering 6 instruments and Trading Pairs within Trading Central FX and Commodities. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Delivered once daily (Pre-London market opening).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br />\n&nbsp;Hourly Live Market Research 24/5</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>&nbsp;Trading Central Instutional level&nbsp;Strategy and Analysis.</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Covering 10 instruments and Trading Pairs within FOREX and Commodities.</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Publication of up to 100 articles per day 24/5.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;Trading Central user friendly content includes actionable comments,directional arrows (green/ red) short&nbsp;comments, key support/ resistance levels, price targets, price chart image.</p>\n\n<h2 dir="ltr">&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<h2 dir="ltr">Safety, Regulation and Reliability</h2>\n\n<p dir="ltr"><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/safety%20of%20funds%281%29.jpg" style="height:235px; line-height:1.6; width:850px" /></p>\n\n<p dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul dir="ltr">\n<li>Trade confidently knowing your funds are safe being held in Tier 1 New Zealand Banks.</li>\n<li>Segregated Client trust Accounts (your funds are not mixed with company funds).</li>\n<li>Strick AML Policies ensure above board compliance for regulators.</li>\n<li>New Zealand Financial Provider License: FSP 403326.</li>\n<li>New Zealand Registered Company Number: 5463921.</li>\n<li>Near instant client deposit and 24 hour withdrawl policy.</li>\n<li>KYC Policy for all new clients and account opening procedures.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p dir="ltr">Simply put as a BlackBull Markets client you get an institutional level of treatment. We are never happy with the status quo but believe in always furthering and bettering ourselves for the benefit of our clients. Our platforms and technologies are in place to make sure our clients retain and have the ability to grow their competitive edge in the global markets.</p>\n\n<p dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2 dir="ltr">Want to trade professionally?</h2>\n\n<p dir="ltr"><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/Market%20Analysis%281%29.jpg" style="height:227px; width:850px" /></p>\n\n<p dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p dir="ltr">At BlackBull we also have programs where, if your trading results meet our requirements, our professional partnered network will offer you more money to trade. &nbsp;This allows you possibilities for jobs at major hedge funds and other trading floors around the world. In a nutshell, other brokers say they want their clients to succeed, but in reality we really have the most to gain from your success. &nbsp;This is why we focus on giving our clients that trading edge.</p>\n\n<p dir="ltr">With our large and rapidly growing firm, we are always implementing and perfecting existing trading technologies while at the same time creating new ways of processing our clients needs in order to give them that edge in the market. &nbsp;We will execute orders at lightning speed through our fiber connected EQUINIX facilities based in the London Financial District. &nbsp;Our clients can feel at home depositing and trading with their local currency wherever they are in the world as we offer 18 deposit currencies.</p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-02-27 00:00:00', ''),
(50, 'Regulation / Legal ', 'regulation-legal', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', ''),
(51, 'Legal Policies', 'legal-policies', 'Forex Trading Legal Policies | BlackBull Compliance', 'BlackBull markets provides security and stability to all the trades with their robust internal legal policies', 'AML, legal policies, Risk Warning, Terms and conditions, Privacy, Dispute Resolution', '', '<p><u>Client Location Policy</u></p>\n\n<p>BlackBull Markets does not accept clients from the USA or from New Zealand, we further do not accept accounts from other high risk&nbsp;OFAC sanctioned nations.</p>\n\n<p>All BlackBull Group Ltd reserves the right to refuse processing a transaction at any stage where it believes the transaction to be connected in any way to money laundering or criminal activity. In accordance with international law, All BlackBull Group Ltd is not obligated to inform the client if suspicious activity is reported to any corresponding regulatory or legal bodies.</p>\n\n<p>While we welcome clients from all over the globe, governmental restrictions along with our company policies prohibit All BlackBull Group Ltd from opening accounts originated from restricted and/or OFAC sanctioned countries.Account Opening Requirements and Framework:</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<u>Photo ID</u> - The following are acceptable forms of photo identification:<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nA valid passport<br />\nA valid government ID, such as a Driver&#39;s License or State ID<br />\nA valid National Identity Card</p>\n\n<p><u>Proof of Residence</u> - The following are acceptable forms of proof of residence:<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nA utility or phone bill, or a bank statement<br />\nAll proof of residences must be current and not outdated by more than 90 days<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<u>Bank Account Requirements</u></p>\n\n<p>All All BlackBull Group Ltd account holders must have a valid bank or credit card account in their name<br />\nThe bank statement should show their name and the same registered address as their application<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Funds Withdrawal Procedures</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\nThe withdrawal process at All BlackBull Group Ltd detailed below, is structured around strict guidelines to make sure that funds are securely sent back to their originating source.&nbsp;All BlackBull Group Ltd customers must complete a signed paper or digital withdrawal request containing their correct account information.&nbsp;The withdrawal form is submitted to the All BlackBull Group Ltd Accounting department for processing. The Accounting department confirms the account balance, verifies that there are no holds or withdrawal restrictions on the account, and then approves the withdrawal request, pending approval by the treasury team.&nbsp;All BlackBull Group Ltd treasury team reviews all withdrawal requests approved by the Accounting department, verifying the original funds are withdrawn via the same method of deposit and to the account holder on file. The treasury team also examines the withdrawal request against the customer&#39;s deposit history to make sure there is no suspicious activity, and verifies the bank account on file.&nbsp;Withdrawal requests approved by the All BlackBull Group Ltd treasury department are sent back to the accounting department, and the funds are released to the client.&nbsp;In the event that a withdrawal is flagged for suspicious activity, the withdrawal is placed on hold, pending further investigation by All BlackBull Group Ltd management staff.<br />\nAll BlackBull Group Ltd Management partners with the treasury team to see if further action needed and which, if any, relevant regulatory bodies need to be contacted.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-02-21 00:00:00', ''),
(52, 'MetaTrader 4 ', 'metatrader-4', 'MetaTrader 4 Forex Trading | MT4 Platform | Exchange ECN Trading - BlackBull Markets', 'MetaTrader 4 is the most famous trading platform, provides trades with edge trading the forex markets with trading tools such as in-depth analysis, live quotes and real-time charts', 'MetaTrader 4 , MT4, Meta quotes , metatrader ', '', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/MT4.png" style="height:306px; width:700px" /></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size:14px">The BlackBull Markets MT4 Trading platform has been designed &nbsp;to provide our clients a <strong>competitive edge</strong> in the modern trading environment. It contains an array of features comprising an <strong>all in one trading solution</strong> from a single program. &nbsp;These include real-time market quotes and live charts on financial data, along with an extensive coverage of current breaking financial news and analytics.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size:14px">These core features contribute to a successful trading experience by using key elements such as management tools, indicators, and expert advisors. &nbsp;The multiple platform and <strong>mobile support</strong> really allows BlackBull Markets MT4 platform to excel in an amazing way for our clients.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size:14px">This platform is purposely built for traders to customize how simple or advanced they want their trading experience to be.&nbsp; It offers an incredibly <strong>user-friendly interface</strong> with a host of a wealthy and vibrant environment and layout leading to the best <strong>performance</strong> from our traders.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size:14px">Being able to view and take control of your portfolio becomes a very easy task with the advanced charting functions.&nbsp; The complex position and order management saves time and effort allowing you to really focus on your trades and the market, without having to worry about multiple programs and news feeds.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size:14px">The BlackBull Markets MT4 platform also allows for automated trading algorithms known as <strong>expert advisers.</strong>&nbsp; These advisors can trade the market for you, but under your control.&nbsp; Clients are able to pick and choose which to install. This allows for the <strong>automated trading strategies</strong> to trade automatically for you <strong>24 hours a day</strong>, 5 days a week, with no intervention necessary.&nbsp; We even provide private server hosting so you don&rsquo;t have to worry about your computer turning off.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size:14px">The <strong>system requirements</strong> for the MT4 platform are below:</span></p>\n\n<ul dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc">\n<li><span style="background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:15px">Windows 2000 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style="background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:15px">Windows XP &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style="background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:15px">Windows Vista</span></li>\n<li><span style="background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:15px">Windows 7</span></li>\n<li><span style="background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:15px">Mac OSX</span></li>\n<li><span style="background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:15px">I phone OS 