(55, 'MetaTrader 4 for Mac OSX', 'metatrader-4-for-mac-ios', '', '', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>At BlackBull Markets you can now download and run our MT4 platform on Mac OSX. &nbsp;Please contact our support team <strong>if you are interesting in using our platform on MAC</strong> and we will happily set it up for you.</p>\n\n<p>The BlackBull Markets MT4 Trading platform has been designed in order to provide our clients a competitive edge in the modern trading environment. It has an array of features comprising of an all in one trading solution from a single program. &nbsp;These include real-time market quotes, live charts on the financial data, and an extensive coverage of current financial news and analytics. &nbsp;These core features contribute to a successful trading experience by using sub features such as management tools, indicators, and expert advisors.&nbsp; This multiple platform along with mobile support really allows the BlackBull Markets MT4 platform to excel in everyway possible for our clients.</p>\n\n<p>This platform is purposely built for traders to customize how simple or advanced they want their trading experience to be.&nbsp; It offers an incredibly user-friendly interface with a host of a wealthy and vibrant layout leading to the best performance from our traders.</p>\n\n<p>Being able to view and take control of your portfolio becomes a very easy task with the advanced charting functions that save time and effort.&nbsp; This allows you to really focus on your trades and the market, without having to worry about multiple programs and news feeds.</p>\n\n<p>The BlackBull Markets MT4 platform also allows for automated trading algorithms known as <strong>expert advisers.</strong>&nbsp; These advisors can trade the market for you, but under your control.&nbsp; Clients are able to pick and choose which to install. &nbsp;This allows for the <strong>automated trading strategies</strong> to trade automatically for you <strong>24 hours a day</strong>, 5 days a week, with no intervention necessary.&nbsp; We even provide private server hosting so you don&rsquo;t have to worry about your computer turning off.</p>\n\n<div>\n<p><strong>Features:<img alt="" src="http://s5.postimg.org/ipp2m30wn/metatrader_4_mac.jpg" style="float:right; height:284px; width:449px" /></strong></p>\n\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Market Watch Window<br />\n&bull; &nbsp;Navigator Window<br />\n&bull; &nbsp;Multiple order types<br />\n&bull; &nbsp;85 pre-installed indicators<br />\n&bull; &nbsp;Analysis tools<br />\n&bull; &nbsp;Multiple chart setups<br />\n&bull; &nbsp;Automated trading<br />\n&bull; &nbsp;Order execution capabilities</p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size:14px"><strong>Benefits:</strong></span><br />\n&bull; &nbsp;Secure trading<br />\n&bull; &nbsp;Real-time data export via DDE protocol<br />\n&bull; &nbsp;First-class charting, with unlimited quantity of charts<br />\n&bull; &nbsp;Free Download<br />\n&bull; &nbsp;Free Demo Account<br />\n&bull; &nbsp;Support for over 18 languages (enquire to see which ones)</p>\n</div>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-03-01 00:00:00', ''),
(56, 'MetaTrader 4 Mobile', 'metatrader-4-mobile', '', '', '', '', '<p>Using mobile trading allows you to manage your trading accounts from devices such as smartphones and tablets wherever you are in the world. &nbsp;The app for BlackBull Markets MT4 offers a great variety of analytical options and graphical display of quotes. &nbsp;In addition, you are able to place and manage orders as if you are on our desktop platform.<img alt="" src="http://s5.postimg.org/lnm1fs8k7/mobile_trading.jpg" style="float:right; line-height:20.7999992370605px" /></p>\n\n<p>Please contact the BlackBull Markets support team<strong>&nbsp;if you are wanting mobile trading,</strong>&nbsp;and we will happily set it up for you.</p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-03-01 00:00:00', ''),
(57, 'MT4 iPhone', 'mt4-iphone', '', '', '', '', '<p>MetaTrader 4 for iPhone/iPad mobile platform is able to impress the traders of all skill levels by its broad capabilities. Fully functional Forex trading, efficient arsenal of the most critical technical analysis tools (30 technical indicators) and ease of use in everyday activities - all these features are available in MetaTrader 4 for iPhone/iPad. You can easily access financial markets from anywhere in the world, at any time and for free.&nbsp;<span style="line-height:1.6">Such possibilities are now available with MetaTrader 4 for iPhone. No compromises are tolerated.</span></p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://s5.postimg.org/ixcpilbvb/aksys_iphone.jpg" style="float:right; line-height:20.7999992370605px" />Please contact the Black Bull Markets support team<strong> if you are wanting mobile trading</strong> and we will set it up for you.</p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-01-28 00:00:00', ''),
(58, 'Myfxbook Auto Trade', 'myfxbook-auto-trade', 'AutoTrade | MyFXBook Automatic Trading Platform - BlackBull Markets', 'BlackBull Markets launches NEXT generation MyFXbook autotrade platform. ', 'Myfxbook, autotrade,  automated trading, ', '', '<p>&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/auto%20trade%20homepage%282%29.jpg" style="height:216px; width:849px" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>BlackBull Markets offers AutoTrade to our clients. &nbsp;This is where you are able to monitor and automatically copy top trader&rsquo;s accounts, and pick out which ones to copy while adjusting how much risk and reward you are willing to take on the fly.</p>\n\n<p>This means that if they (the trader of your choosing) place a trade, autotrade will automatically place the same trade on your account as long as you have selected them to follow their trades. &nbsp;&nbsp;It&rsquo;s as easy as clicking &quot;autotrade&quot; which you can see below. You do not need to download any additional software, just follow the instructions from our support staff to enable your account to autotrade. &nbsp;&nbsp;We will happily walk you through the process.</p>\n\n<p>You can manually close other trader&rsquo;s trades at any time on your regular MT4 platform, as well as placing your own trades. &nbsp;The best part is that we do not charge any extra for auto trade. &nbsp;It is worth noting that a balance of $1000 or more is needed to safely begin to autotrade.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; %%create-auto-trade-account-here-rpicu8vj%%</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:14px">Below you can see part of the selection of traders you will be able to auto trade:</span></p>\n\n<p><a href="http://postimg.org/image/s8lupj5n7/"><img alt="" src="http://s5.postimg.org/5jwnpyo9j/auto_systems.jpg" /></a></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Once you identify one or more that you like, simply click on the name and it will bring you to a <strong>more detailed page of their results</strong> so you can identify if they will suit your need or not.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://s5.postimg.org/coegyzviv/click_here_auto_t.jpg" /></p>\n\n<p>Finally if everything looks suitable, follow the <strong>green arrow on the photo above and click on auto trade. &nbsp;</strong>This will bring you to the page below where you can change your risk settings and automatically begin copying trades to your account.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://s5.postimg.org/i8vjndjrr/auto_select.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Once you click on <strong>OK</strong> down the bottom, the trades will automatically be copied to your BlackBull Markets MT4 account. &nbsp;To stop copying trades from the traders is as simple as clicking <strong>Unsubscribe</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://s5.postimg.org/b87julhzr/manage_auto_trade.jpg" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Clicking on Simulate Auto Trade will bring you to the below link where you can select and c<strong>ompare&nbsp;hypothetical results from past trades of systems</strong> available to you.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>You can<strong> simulate the deposit amount</strong> and the <strong>time frame,</strong> then <strong>compare each system</strong> on the graph below before <strong>saving it and applying</strong> the exact settings to your real account later.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://s5.postimg.org/4kay7zyhj/custom_auto_sim.jpg" /></p>\n\n<p>You can also see how it works in action with a free BlackBull Demo account.</p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-03-06 00:00:00', ''),
(59, 'Virtual Private Servers', 'virtual-private-servers', 'FREE Forex VPS Trading for Robot | Virtual Private Server - BlackBull Markets EA Trading', 'BlackBull Markets provides FREE VPS trading for expert advisor and robots. To apply for FREE Virtual private Server, apply and qualify from the BlackBull markets website. This allows you to trade from anywhere in the world', 'VPS, Virtual Private Server, EA, Expert Advisor, Robot Trading, Automatic Trading, remote trading', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/vps.jpg" style="height:221px; width:850px" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>At BlackBull Markets we offer free VPS hosting for all Metatrader 4 live accounts.&nbsp;&nbsp; If your balance is over $2000 USD, we will provide this at no additional cost for you.&nbsp; This allows you to stop relying on your home computer when trading and running expert advisors.&nbsp; If you have below the minimum required balance, you can simply pay for it each month by having funds taken directly out of your trading account.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>&nbsp;Free VPS service with LIVE funded account.</li>\n<li>&nbsp;LOW latency - ultra millsecond execution speeds.</li>\n<li>&nbsp;24/7 access from anywhere in the world. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Perfect environment for EA trading.</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Cross Connected to BlackBull Technology Infrastructure. &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family:open sans,helvetica,arial,sans-serif">%%apply-now-yop9mvyp%%</span>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style="color:rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family:open sans,helvetica,arial,sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-02-28 00:00:00', ''),
