(67, 'Deposit Funds', 'deposit-funds', 'Multiple Deposit Options | Fast Deposit | Multiple Deposit Currency - BlackBull Markets', 'Please ensure the name of the bank account from which funds are sent matches the name of your BlackBull Markets.', 'Multiple deposit currency, blackbull markets, deposit funds', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/safe%20deposit.jpg" style="height:216px; width:850px" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size:14px">Funding is as easy with BlackBull Markets. There are multiple methods and choices with us for you to fund your account. Be it credit/ debit, bank wire or any method of your choice, we have it for you.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size:14px">The following deposit methods are also avaliable from our client portal once you have created a live account:</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size:14px">We accept all of the following deposit currencies:</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size:14px">United States dollar (USD), Euro (EUR), Great British Pound (GBP), Japanese Yen (JPY), Australian Dollar (AUD) , New Zealand Dollar (NZD), Singapore Dollar (SGD) and the Canadian Dollar (CAD).</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size:14px">Aside from bank wire which takes 1-3 days to process all other payment methods are instant allowing &nbsp;you to manage your account in real time.</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size:18px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Skrill &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;China Union Pay &nbsp; &nbsp;Visa &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;MasterCard &nbsp; &nbsp; WebMoney &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;BankWire &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Neteller&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/skrill.jpg" style="height:58px; width:100px" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/union%20pay.jpg" style="height:81px; width:100px" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/visa.jpg" style="height:81px; width:100px" />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/mastercard.jpg" style="height:81px; width:100px" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/webmoney.jpg" style="height:81px; width:100px" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/bank%20wire.jpg" style="height:81px; width:100px" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/netteller.jpg" style="height:81px; width:100px" /></p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-03-09 00:00:00', ''),
(68, 'Withdrawals ', 'withdrawals', 'Quick Withdrawal Process | Instant Withdrawal - BlackBull markets', '', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/credit-cards-cash.jpg" style="height:228px; width:850px" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>BlackBull Markets has a very strick withdrawl policy where all requests must be processed in under 24 hours for our clients&nbsp;convenience and peace of mind.&nbsp;It is important to us that our clients have access to their funds as quickly and as reliably as possible.</p>\n\n<h2>How to withdraw by Wire Transfer?</h2>\n\n<p>Existing account holders must simply log in to theclient portal area and select Withdraw Funds/ Wire Transfer. U</p>\n\n<p>pon clicking, a secure withdrawal form will open where existing account holders can enter their Wire Transfer details. Please note that Wire Transfer takes 3-5 days for the funds to arrive in your account.</p>\n\n<p>Minimum Withdrawal Amount through Wire Transfer is 100 USD.</p>\n\n<p>BlackBull Markets does not charge for sending wire payments, however transfer fees are applied by our remitting bank(s) or payment system provider. Withdrawals are processed within two business days of receipt of this form. Forms submitted with missing information are subject to delay.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2>Withdrawl by our Payment Partners i.e Skrill, Moneybookers.</h2>\n\n<p>Simply submit a withdrawl request in our client portal and once it has been approved (within 24 hours) the withdrawl amount requested will be deposited into your account.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2>How to withdraw by Credit Card?</h2>\n\n<p>BlackBull Markets accepts withdrawals from trading accounts by credit cards (Visa, MasterCard ).</p>\n\n<p>Trading account holders must be logged in to the BlackBull be able to withdraw. Be informed that withdrawals by credit cards can only be processed to the exact same card used to deposit at BlackBull Markets.</p>\n\n<p>The maximum amount that can be sent is the amount of deposit.</p>\n\n<p>Profits or amounts in excess of the deposit amount can only be processed by Wire Transfer. Please note that Credit Card Withdrawals take 3-5 days for the funds to arrive in your account.<br />\nMinimum Withdrawal Amount through Credit Card is 10 USD.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/skrill.jpg" style="height:58px; width:100px" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/union%20pay.jpg" style="height:81px; width:100px" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/visa.jpg" style="height:81px; width:100px" />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/mastercard.jpg" style="height:81px; width:100px" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/webmoney.jpg" style="height:81px; width:100px" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/bank%20wire.jpg" style="height:81px; width:100px" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/netteller.jpg" style="height:81px; width:100px" /></p>', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-03-09 00:00:00', ''),
