(70, 'MT4 Android', 'mt4-android', '', '', '', '', '<p><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">BlackBull Markets MetaTrader 4 Forex trading technologies can now be downloaded on the devices powered by the popular Android OS. Complete set of trade orders, trading history, interactive charts and the widest selection of supported mobile devices - all that is MetaTrader 4 for Android. Wherever you are and whatever you do, Forex will always be with you. Integrated charts will help you to determine the current dynamics of symbol quotes, trading history will show you all your previous deals, while the powerful trading system will allow you to perform new ones. And all this can be done on the move.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><img alt="" src="http://s5.postimg.org/nhyvxivkn/mobile_mt4_android_1.jpg" style="float:right; height:215px; width:300px" /></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">Please contact the Black Bull Markets support team<strong>&nbsp;if you are wanting mobile trading</strong>&nbsp;and we will set it up for you.</span></p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-01-28 00:00:00', ''),
(71, 'MT4 Blackberry', 'mt4-blackberry', '', '', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>BlackBull Markets MT4 platform for BlackBerry allows free mobile trading for all new and existing BlackBull Markets clients. &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://s5.postimg.org/n7rde6gyf/blackberry.png" style="float:right" /></p>\n\n<p><u>BlackBull Markets MT4 platform enables:</u> &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>- Trading from a live tick chart</p>\n\n<p>- using all available instruments</p>\n\n<p>- placing buy, sell and pending orders</p>\n\n<p>- setting stop loss and take profit</p>\n\n<p>- closing and modifying open orders</p>\n\n<p>- viewing current result of open trades</p>\n\n<p>- viewing trading history</p>\n\n<p>- viewing real-time charts</p>\n\n<p>- viewing real-time market prices &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>- using Fibonacci Retracement calculator</p>\n\n<p>- using Pivot Point calculator</p>\n\n<p>- using Profit Calculator</p>\n\n<p><span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Please contact the Black Bull Markets support team</span><strong>&nbsp;if you are wanting mobile trading</strong><span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">&nbsp;and we will set it up for you.</span></p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-01-28 00:00:00', ''),
(72, ' Regulation & Compliance', 'regulation-compliance', 'Forex Regulated License | BlackBull Markets - Registered FSP Broker', 'BlackBull Markets is a Regulated Broker and registered with Financial Service Provider, FSP based in the heart of Auckland Central , New Zealand', 'BlackBull Markets, forex broker, forex trading, Auckland, New Zealand, London, UK ', '', '<p><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/Account%281%29.jpg" style="height:309px; width:850px" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>BlackBull Markets is a New Zealand Registered Company and hold a Financial Services Provider (FSP) license. We have a strict AML policy to make sure our Brokerage runs above board in all aspects of our business.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>BlackBull Markets does not take on board US or NZ clients</p>\n\n<p>New Zealand Company Number: 5463921<br />\nFinancial Service Provider : FSP403326</p>\n\n<p>Client Funds are all held in segregated bank accounts in top Tier international banks to provide you with the comfort and control over your investment.</p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-02-26 00:00:00', ''),
(73, 'Account Types', 'account-types', 'Trading Account Types | Standard | Prime | Institutional - BlackBull markets', '', 'trading account types, forex trading, ECN spreads', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://s28.postimg.org/67ks7zd31/account_types_v2.png" /></p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-02-21 00:00:00', ''),
(74, 'Islamic Account', 'islamic-account', 'Swap Free Trading Account | Sharia Law | Islamic Trading - BlackBull markets', '', 'swap free trading , sharia law, Islamic trading', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="http://s17.postimg.org/dn7xdyszj/logo.jpg" style="height:211px; width:484px" /></p>\n\n<p>BlackBull Markets is committed to providing its clients with the best institutional trading conditions it can. To this end we now offer 5 different accounts to suit the specific requirements of different traders.</p>\n\n<p><span style="line-height:1.6">Whether you are looking to open a Demo or Live account, with a Standard, BlackBull Prime, VIP or Islamic account you will find the complete flexibility to trade at the level you want. Whatever your trading strategy, level of funding or appetite for risk, from micro to unlimited trade sizes, there is an account to suit your needs perfectly.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="line-height:1.6">The three Islamic account types available to replicate the BlackBull Markets Standard, BlackBull Prime and VIP accounts but with the key feature of no SWAP being applied. Every other feature of the account remains the same and if you are looking to fund in a currency not offered please speak to support and we can see if a personal banking solution can be found wherever you are in the world.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="line-height:1.6">Please contact support@blackbullmarkets.com for more information and how we can set your account up for your needs.</span></p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-03-07 00:00:00', ''),
(76, ' Introducing Broker', 'introducing-broker', 'Introducing Broker Program | Competitive IB Commission - BlackBull Institutional ', 'BlackBull Markets Introducing Broker (IB) program is available to financial reward to  introducers with no limits on the number of referred accounts or trading volumes. An attractive rebate program\nlicensed and Regulated Broker', 'IB , Introducing broker, IB commission, partnership', '', '<div><img alt="" src="http://s5.postimg.org/p35ud2cev/introducing_forex_broker.jpg" style="height:199px; width:880px" /></div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>\n<p><strong>BlackBull Markets Introducing Broker (IB) program</strong>&nbsp;is available to financially reward&nbsp;introducers with no limits on the number of referred accounts or trading volumes. &nbsp;The setup is easy to begin and has a highly competitive volume based rebate structure.&nbsp; This makes BlackBull Markets ideal for introducers big and small. &nbsp;The IB program is perfect if you have a Forex content website, forum, or a group of traders that you would like to help get setup with BlackBull markets.&nbsp; Most IBs are able to get a steady income stream by introducing or referring just a handful of clients a month to BlackBull Markets.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="background-color:rgb(248, 248, 248); color:rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family:open sans,helvetica,arial,sans-serif">%%ib-text-mye05ves%%&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Key features of our Introducing Broker program:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>An attractive rebate program</li>\n<li>Licensed and Regulated Broker</li>\n<li>Personal IB account managers</li>\n<li>Simple client onboarding and commission tracking through our portal</li>\n<li>MetaTrader 4 &amp; Mobile Trading Platforms</li>\n<li>Commissions paid into a trading account</li>\n<li>Marketing material in a variety of different languages around the world</li>\n<li>Advanced cookie tracking and web reporting</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>A&nbsp;<strong>Professional Introducing Broker</strong>&nbsp;has the added benefit of applying spread and commission mark-ups to earn additional revenue from their clients trading activity. &nbsp;This edition is specifically designed for Introducers with greater than ten clients, and who provide additional value/services to their clients.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Examples of Eligible Professional Introducing Broker&rsquo;s include:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Licensed Investment Advisors</li>\n<li>EA Vendors/Developers</li>\n<li>Money Managers</li>\n<li>Website owners</li>\n<li>Trading Educators</li>\n<li>Hosting Sub IBs</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style="color:rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family:open sans,helvetica,arial,sans-serif">%%quick-ib-form-qudm7h4s-3%/%</span></p>\n</div>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-03-01 00:00:00', ''),
(77, 'Careers', 'careers', 'Careers in Financial Services| Forex with BlackBull Markets                                                    ', 'BlackBull Group provides fast paced and innovative work place. ', 'Financial Services, Forex trading careers, Work-Life balance, fast paced environment', '', '<p><img alt="" src="http://www.blackbullmarkets.com/ed.images/images/careers.jpg" style="height:205px; width:850px" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>BlackBull Markets is rapidly becoming one of the major players in the industry and due to our growth are always looking for talented individuals who have experience and qualifications in banking, legal and financial sales. Please email your CV and what kind of role you are hoping for to support@backbullmarkets.com and we will get back to you.</p>\n\n<p>We are also offer internships for students looking to gain some experience in the industry so if you are a hard working individual please send us your CV as well.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Benefits of working with BlackBull Group Limited</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Great Work-Life balance</li>\n<li>Inspires Innovation and Creativity</li>\n<li>Excellent Package - Compensation and Benefits</li>\n<li>Team Culture</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', '', 1, 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '2015-02-21 00:00:00', ''),
